name: Jeroen Webb (V)
Lore: 'Native of Ralltiir. Spy for Ralltiir''s underground network after his homeworld was subjugated.',
Text: 'If deploying to opponent''s mobile site, deploys as an Undercover spy (deploy -2). Nevar Yalnal may not target spies at Webb''s site. Opponent''s total influence here is -1 for each of your spies at sites.',
